    <item>
      <title>The British way of dealing with foreign APIs.</title>
      <link>http://codeinthehole.com/tidbits/the-british-way-of-dealing-with-foreign-apis/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Feb 2011 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://codeinthehole.com/tidbits/the-british-way-of-dealing-with-foreign-apis/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;A bad joke told in Python:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34; style=&#34;background: #272822&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;line-height: 125%&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #66d9ef&#34;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #a6e22e&#34;&gt;call_foreign_api&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #f8f8f2&#34;&gt;(str):&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #66d9ef&#34;&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #f8f8f2&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span style=&#34;color: #f8f8f2&#34;&gt;foreign_api(str)&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span style=&#34;color: #66d9ef&#34;&gt;except&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #f8f8f2&#34;&gt;NotUnderstoodError:&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span style=&#34;color: #f8f8f2&#34;&gt;foreign_api(str&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #f92672&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #f8f8f2&#34;&gt;upper())&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
